      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic, a dedicated hobbyist, or as a parts donor. It currently has major mechanical challenges, including a failing head gasket and a transmission that slips significantly when shifting into higher gears. The exterior shows its age with several deep dents, significant rust on the rocker panels, and peeling paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and the air conditioning is non-functional. It will likely require a tow to its new home, but it offers a solid foundation of salvageable components for the right project.",
