    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken obsessive care of it, and it\u2019s been tucked away in a garage its whole life. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. You really have to see it in person to believe how spotless it is! I'm looking for a smooth sale, so feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43250.0,
