    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade A80 Supra Turbo in pristine, factory-original condition. This specimen features the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six, retaining its sequential twin-turbocharger setup and unmodified forced induction plumbing. The drivetrain is anchored by the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission, transferring power to a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original double-wishbone geometry with factory-spec dampers, providing the precise kinematic response intended by Toyota engineers. All body panels bear matching VIN tags, and the undercarriage shows zero signs of oxidation or structural fatigue. A rare, unmolested example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
